Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.20,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為嚮往卡萊多劇團獨自一人來到美國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.90,0:00:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其多想還是先做比較符合我的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會放棄正在做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻總能幸運地完成做不了的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.20,0:00:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必要的時候決不放棄！決不！決不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.50,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家能不能好好和父母說過自己的心事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.50,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道是自己想的太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.80,0:00:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我還是不想讓自己後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.70,0:00:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是想說出自己的真實想法呢！呢！呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有10分鐘開演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，你奶奶的手術怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才接到電話，手術很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，謝……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要是再不加油的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~要是不幹些奇怪的事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會緊張的腦子一片空白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空和我們就不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有上臺的經驗，真是輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不是那樣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用特地打扮成這種樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒你說的那麼可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問，卡萊多劇團……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真好運啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是從日本來的空的初演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空是我的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人驚喜的表演還在後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.70,0:04:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開演還有段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位諒解，稍安勿噪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不能出錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天客人超滿座哦，加油啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超……滿座？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對……對不起了\N讓你們緊張了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上沒有不讓人緊張的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.40,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是啊\N蕾拉小姐他們也緊張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記你們是勉強合格的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……不用特地送我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和空是什麼關係啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蕾拉小姐\N表演的那麼自如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不知道表演了多少次\N才積累的舞臺經驗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是蕾拉小姐厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比練習的時候的表演更生動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是專業的表演強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.70,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐的歌唱結束後\N就是你們魔法使登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大膽點去表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡自己所能就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調勻呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，使出我們的魔法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的三重影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我上場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧和燈光準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐提前上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行，笑臉笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算這麼對觀眾解釋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，對不起，是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我沒有配合好\N蕾拉小姐的提前出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，有客人找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空……空的父親？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來帶空回去的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父母一直都反對\N空進卡萊多劇團的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，這二位\N是和我同時入團的美亞和阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們照顧空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會突然來這裏呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.30,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，突然到這裏來出差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，這位是健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面，請……請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天\N謝謝爸爸來看我的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵，看到了奇怪的表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習的時候不小心摔到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那今天住在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帶您出去逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了\N晚上去飯店吃日本飯菜怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N但是和美亞她們約好了練習的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不過我還是很想吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.20,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒吃日本飯菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也來看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.30,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的父母不是親生父母吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像夾住我的頭髮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得父親來看我，要加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被說的真慘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼還能繼續嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？有不詳的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天那場劇目的報導啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團公演的新作劇目中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉的絕技引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使一值由三人演出是個失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演技也不夠精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了那種事\N今天觀眾該怎麼看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，提起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓報導給左右了情緒\N還怎麼表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的那些失誤\N都由我來彌補好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞也是，阿娜也是\N比昨天跳的還低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.00,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，聽說那個魔法使的角色\N居報導批評的一無是處呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，蕾拉好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都幹了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是那種狀態的話\N現在就可以退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是場表現魔法的高潮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.70,0:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也能上臺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回日本吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來是想看看你的情況的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也很擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你在這裏很辛苦\N媽媽想讓你跟我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是爸爸更反對些就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初說可以讓你\N去卡萊多劇團的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時絕對應該留下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼危險的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不想再看到你這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不回去的話\N爸爸也不回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你總不回來，所以來找你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸都說了些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我……回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，你不會回去的，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能對爸爸說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為……因為……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.70,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起，叔叔阿姨\N就是空的爸爸媽媽了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.30,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的親生父母在我入小學之前\N就死於交通事故了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的父親\N是我親生父親的表兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是親生的父親\N就不能說些任性的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.60,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母對於我是精心撫養的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能說“不想回去”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.20,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說就說吧，空的真實感情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸病倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波力士先生帶來的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸現在\N在凱普美利醫院裏接受治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，表演馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不去的話……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不參加表演的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能這次再也得不到原諒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.20,0:16:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時候蕾拉\N可能正像平時一樣站在舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能會因此而看不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是對我來說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心，很安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和爸爸一起回日本吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想和爸爸媽媽在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙算怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她爸爸……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.30,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼事\N都不能成為缺席的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是誰來代演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使的角色就她們二人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉，靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為道歉就可以了事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定退出卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼能說會道\N還以外你真的很有能耐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎感到很遺憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在開玩笑吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再重新考慮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.90,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，但是我已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空不在的話\N那個角色演不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在向老闆道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個角色沒有我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸和媽媽的孩子\N就只有我一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間很短\N還是登上了卡萊多的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思緒起伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，煩惱消除之後將不再迷茫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在這邊多住院觀察下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空肯回去了，我的身體也好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次來看卡萊多的表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎麼樣？有趣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐很厲害吧\N由利先生也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想能和他們\N站在同一個舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.20,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸答應我能通過試演\N就同意我入團的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被錄取後\N爸爸說了“恭喜你”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚爸爸媽媽\N都反對我入團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.20,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以爸爸能來看我\N真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來想給爸爸看更好的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想放棄卡萊多的演藝生涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.10,0:20:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不想讓爸爸和媽媽擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，爸爸一個人回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.10,0:21:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是過於辛苦的話一定要回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我們最寶貝的女兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心自己的傷口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天說了那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.90,0:21:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是\N喜歡卡萊多的演藝生涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.80,0:21:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我一次機會，求您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須道歉的物件不是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的債主是\N那些特地來看我們表演的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一場的表演你要加倍奉還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.90,0:22:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天，我要讓\N爸爸媽媽自豪地來看我的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.70,0:23:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，我們撿了個小海狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.90,0:23:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就叫它喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.00,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能在劇團裏養動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說得我們自己養\N可也要飼料啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人只能參加\N魔術比賽奪取優勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.50,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
